Package it.unitn.disi.smatch.loaders

Interface Summary
ILoader Interface allowing to load contexts from various representations such as files, DBs, etc
IMappingLoader Interface for mapping loaders.
 

Class Summary
CTXML Parses CTXML files and serves as a file filter for .xml files.
CTXMLLoader Loader for CTXML format.
PlainMappingLoader Loads only mapping part, as written by PlainRenderer.java
TABLoader Loads context from a tab-separated file.
